snippet.title: DELTARUNE Nintendo Switch 2 Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
DELTARUNE Chapters 1-4 will be released on June 5 as a launch title for Nintendo Switch 2 (TM). It's also coming to Steam, Switch, PS4, and PS5 the same day! For more info, visit: https://www.deltarune.com
Trailer by Everdraed
Sepia Animation by Temmie Chang
Music composed by Toby Fox + additional arrangement & production by Camellia
DELTARUNE © Toby Fox 2018-2025. All rights reserved.
